    "description": "In Cat Souls, you will be playing as Ruby, an energetic cat with a strange ability. Like all cats, Ruby has more than one life, but not all of them can use their past souls as a platform.<br><br>Ruby and her friend went on an adventure and successfully found the mythical Hourglass of time! Sadly the end of that adventure is the beginning of a new one.<br><br>Enemies appeared out of nowhere, and our protagonists tried to run but… only Ruby managed to escape. But she still has 7 lives! Now is the time to rescue your friend and get the Hourglass of Time back!<br><br>Jump, avoid obstacles, use levers, and collect keys to reach the end of each level in time. The spikes will only take one of your lives, but be careful not to waste them all!<br><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>45 levels<br></li><li>Fun soul game mechanic<br></li><li>Different obstacles and enemies<br></li><li>6 different worlds<br></li><li>2D Platformer<br></li><li>Cute pixel art</li></ul>",
